$learning_note.value: The video titled "Quiz Blitz Guess The Voice and The Song! Disney Edition!" is a fun and engaging challenge that tests viewers' knowledge of Disney characters and songs. Participants are prompted to identify the voices and songs of various Disney characters, such as Anxiety from "Inside Out 2," Elsa, Moana, Simba, and many others. The quiz includes a mix of character voices and songs, encouraging fans to recall their favorite Disney moments and characters. This interactive format not only entertains but also serves as a nostalgic journey through Disney's rich history of animated films and beloved characters.
